<li><cite style="font-style:normal" class="book" id="CITEREFReich1974">Reich, Steve (1974). <i>Writings About Music</i>. Halifax: Press of the <a href="/wiki/Nova_Scotia_College_of_Art_and_Design" title="Nova Scotia College of Art and Design" class="mw-redirect">Nova Scotia College of Art and Design</a>. pp.&#160;78. <a href="/wiki/Special:BookSources/091961602X" class="internal">ISBN 0-919616-02-x</a>.</cite><span class="Z3988" title="ctx_ver=Z39.88-2004&amp;rft_val_fmt=info%3Aofi%2Ffmt%3Akev%3Amtx%3Abook&amp;rft.genre=book&amp;rft.btitle=Writings+About+Music&amp;rft.aulast=Reich&amp;rft.aufirst=Steve&amp;rft.au=Reich%2C+Steve&amp;rft.date=1974&amp;rft.pages=pp.%26nbsp%3B78&amp;rft.place=Halifax&amp;rft.pub=Press+of+the+%5B%5BNova+Scotia+College+of+Art+and+Design%5D%5D&amp;rft.isbn=0-919616-02-x&amp;rfr_id=info:sid/en.wikipedia.org:Steve_Reich"><span style="display: none;">&#160;</span></span></li>
